  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "Hardhat fails to import `.sol` files from a git repository dependency that does not have a `package.json`.\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n```bash\r\nyarn add --dev https://github.com/abdk-consulting/abdk-libraries-solidity/\r\n```\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\nimport 'abdk-libraries-solidity/ABDKMath64x64.sol'\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis import fails, unless a `package.json` is added to `node_modules/abdk-libraries-solidity`:\r\n```json\r\n{}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThere is no obvious reason for this restriction, and it should be removed if possible.",
